# Max Uint16

> Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

<!-- <usage> -->

## Usage

``` javascript
var UINT16_MAX = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/uint16-max' );
```

#### UINT16_MAX

Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

``` javascript
UINT16_MAX === 65535;
```

<!-- </usage> -->
